    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You fill your insects with an intense surge of Chakra enhancing their overall potential and abilities</p><p>For the duration, when you would cast an Aburame Hijutsu that deals damage, its increase is increased by +1 damage die and now adds your ninjutsu ability modifier if it did not already.</p><p>Additionally, if an Aburame Hijutsu you cast would increase the base cost of a creatures jutsu, that base cost penalty is increased by an amount equal to the rank of the Hijutsu cast. (D-Rank: +4, C-Rank: +6, B-Rank: +8, A- Rank: +10, S-Rank: +12)</p>",
